Interface ReportColumnHeader<Item extends QueryItem>

  • Type Parameters:
    Item - QueryItem on which the Report is based on.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TaskStatusColumnHeader, TimeIntervalColumnHeader

    public interface ReportColumnHeader<Item extends QueryItem>
    A ReportColumnHeader is an element of a Report. It determines weather a given <Item> belongs into the representing column.
